      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older vehicle in fair overall condition and priced accordingly. It shows normal age and use, with visible cosmetic wear on the exterior and an interior that is used but still serviceable. This is not a pristine example, but it should appeal to someone looking for a decent driver at a realistic price. Expect some deferred maintenance and the kind of minor issues that come with an older car, so buyers should plan on giving it the attention a vehicle of this age typically needs.",
