    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Affordable, honest fair-condition car that\u2019s ready to be used and enjoyed as a practical driver. It starts, runs, and drives, and it offers solid value for someone looking for usable transportation without paying for a perfect example. Not a mint show car, but a straightforward, decent vehicle with plenty of life left for the next owner.",
