    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Well-kept and ready to enjoy, this is a clean, honest car in good condition that presents nicely inside and out. It drives well, has clearly been cared for, and should make a great choice for someone looking for a quality example without paying top-dollar for a mint one. A sharp, appealing car with plenty to like.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
