      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Like-new mint-condition used car that has clearly been exceptionally well cared for. The exterior presents beautifully with a very clean finish, strong shine, and little to no noticeable cosmetic wear, while the interior is equally impressive with clean surfaces, minimal signs of use, and a well-kept overall feel. This is the kind of vehicle a buyer can expect to be proud to own immediately, with a premium presentation inside and out and no meaningful age-related wear standing out. A very sharp, well-preserved example for someone looking for a top-condition used car.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for a buyer looking for low-cost transportation or a solid project. It shows its age and wear, but it remains an appealing value for someone who appreciates an honest, budget-minded purchase with plenty of potential. Priced to sell and well-suited for a cash buyer seeking maximum affordability.",
      "price": 4495.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it still has plenty of charm and could make a great budget runabout, first project, or practical backup vehicle. If you\u2019re after something inexpensive, straightforward, and worth a look, this one could be a really handy buy.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with strong project potential. The powertrain pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to enjoy on the road. Cosmetic wear, age-related blemishes, and general rough edges are present, but this is the kind of mechanically straightforward car that rewards a hands-on owner. Good candidate for a daily beater, shop runabout, or weekend restoration starting point. Priced to reflect condition while still offering a lot of usable car for the money.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    }
